kunagi üldse on olnud!

314
00:41:24,691 --> 00:41:28,784
Mul on sulle hirmutavaid uudiseid.

315
00:41:29,829 --> 00:41:33,426
Mis saab sellest
veel hirmutavam olla?

316
00:41:33,566 --> 00:41:37,591
Su jutt kõlab nagu
sul oleks juba parem.

317
00:41:38,037 --> 00:41:41,027
Vasta mulle ausalt, palun.

318
00:41:41,241 --> 00:41:44,509
Kas ei ole hea ennast paremini tunda?

319
